Fundraising
15/11/2018 « Tous Nobels ! », an ambitious campaign!

   The University of Strasbourg and Strasbourg University Hospital are
   launching a new fundraising campaign to raise €50 million by 2022. An
   unprecedented operation in the French public academic world.
