20/11/2018 Exceptional meeting with DuPont

   On November 13, 2018 at the University of Strasbourg. Dr. Simone
   ARIZZZI, Technology & Innovation Director, presented the challenges to
   be met in order to maintain innovation at the highest level of
   requirement and develop solutions that will meet the challenges of
   tomorrow.
