A word from our Chairman

   Bernard Meunier, Chairman of the Académie des Sciences and the Frontier
   Research in Chemistry Foundation
   The Frontier Research in Chemistry  Foundation (Fondation pour la
   Recherche en Chimie) drives progress in a bid to tackle the scientific,
   industrial and societal challenges of the 21st century.  After 10 years
   of successful, committed work helping businesses and researchers, the
   foundation is open to anyone who wants to work with us on innovative,
   progressive...

